There are - there is the explosion of co-working spaces.
In Italy we have some wonderful success stories on this issue.
Smart working has become a theme at the heart of corporate strategies.
The observatory on smart working of the Politecnico di Milano claims that most companies in Milan have now adopted smart working strategies.
